OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA grey start in places but
OL,6,Fsunny spells quickly developing
OL,7,Fleading to a largely dry and bright
OL,8,Fday. Throughout the afternoon cloud
OL,9,Fwill build with some showers moving
OL,10,Finto the northeast by dusk. Warm in
OL,11,Fany sunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers clearing to the south
OL,14,Fleaving a dry end to the evening. Low
OL,15,Fcloud will then move in from the east
OL,16,Fovernight with perhaps some patchy
OL,17,Fdrizzle by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
