OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FRather grey with perhaps the
OL,6,Fodd spot of light rain initially,
OL,7,Fespecially over the hills. Some
OL,8,Fsunshine developing later in the day,
OL,9,Fbut feeling cooler than of late.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FEarly
OL,12,Fmorning cloud on Wednesday and
OL,13,FThursday quickly lifting to leave
OL,14,Fplenty of sunshine both days. Risk of
OL,15,Fshowers come Friday but feeling
OL,16,Fincreasingly warmer and more humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
